In the NASCAR Chase for the Sprint Cup's first ever elimination round, Jeff Gordon wins the 2014 AAA 400 at Dover International Speedway while Kurt Busch, A. J. Allmendinger, Greg Biffle and Aric Almirola are eliminated from championship contention. (ESPN)The NHL Draft is held at the BB&T Center with the Edmonton Oilers selecting Connor McDavid as their number 1 pick. (Bleacher Report)